msgid ""
"the :math:`I` state node is recovered to the :math:`S` state with "
"probability :math:`\\gamma` (I→S)."
msgstr ":math:`I ' 状态节点恢复到:math:`S ' 状态,概率为:math:``\\gamma ' (I S)."

